  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "The [resolve](https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle/blob/develop/packages/resolver/lib/resolver.ts#L70) method queries different sources to resolve a file. In the case of `console.log`, this causes the file to be re-loaded from disk every time during the truffle-command process. This can be cached for faster resolution. There are other truffle assets that could benefit from this technique.\r\n\r\nThis was discovered during review of #5687 ",
